    "Thus, the system has a 100% chance of being measured in the state |00⟩ and no chance of being measured in the states |01⟩, |10⟩, or |11⟩.|𝜓 ⟩ =In more complex quantum systems, with more qubits involved, sets of qubits can be conceptually grouped into quantum registers.",
